title: MoMA presents retrospective on artist Joaquin Torres-Garcia
text:
> Entertainment MoMA presents retrospective on artist Joaquin Torres-Garcia "Untitled," one of the works of artist Joaquin Torres-Garcia, is displayed during a preview of a retrospective of his work, at the Museum of Modern Art, in New York, Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015.
